SPDX expression: ``Apache-2.0 OR GPL-2.0-or-later``.

Recipient picks. Most consumers — including merchants embedding
the sidecar in their own infrastructure — will find Apache-2.0
sufficient. The GPL-2.0-or-later option exists for cross-
ecosystem consistency with the broader OpenSalesTax portfolio
(the WooCommerce, Bagisto, and Odoo connectors all carry a dual
or copyleft option for the same redistribution reasons).

